high_descs: Turn right and move to stand between the television and coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper from the bottom shelf of the coffee table.
Carry the newspaper while moving to stand between the sofa and coffee table, facing the sofa.
Place the newspaper to the right of the pillow on the rightmost cushion.
Move to stand in front of the television.
Pick up the newspaper from the shelf beneath the television.
Turn and carry the newspaper to the point where you're facing the sofa again, standing between the sofa and coffee table.
Place the newspaper on the rightmost cushion behind the other newspaper you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two newspapers to the sofa.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper on the table.
Walk around the table to look at the couch.
Place the newspaper on the couch to the right of the pillow.
Turn around and walk to the TV stand.
Pick up the newspaper on the bottom shelf of the TV stand.
Turn around and walk back around the coffee table to the couch.
Place the newspaper behind the first newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Place two newspapers on a couch.

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the sofa, turn right and go between the TV stand and coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper that's on the coffee table.
Go around the coffee table and head towards the black sofa.
Place the newspaper on the bottom right corner of the sofa.
Turn around and head towards the TV stand.
Pick up the newspaper from the bottom left of the TV stand.
Turn around and return to the black sofa.
Put the newspaper next to the pillow.
anns.task_desc: Find two newspapers and place them on the black sofa.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table that is in the middle of the room in front of you
Pick up the newspaper that is on the second shelf.
Walk over to the couch that is in front of you
Place newspaper on the right couch cushion
Turn around and walk to the TV that is directly in front of you
Pick up the newspaper that is on the bottom shelf
Turn around and walk to the couch that is in front of you
Place newspaper on the right couch cushion above the newspaper that's already there.
